{"title":"绘图和数据存储原理","date":"2020-11-30T01:22:20.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年11月30日","L":"2020/11/30","MM-DD":"11-30"},"link":"posts/1b3d4e9a","comments":true,"tags":["HTML5+CSS3"],"categories":["网页设计"],"updated":"2020-11-30T01:38:02.437Z","content":"<h1 id=\"javascript的引入\">JavaScript的引入<a href=\"#javascript的引入\" title=\"JavaScript的引入\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"行内式\">行内式<a href=\"#行内式\" title=\"行内式\"></a></h2><ul><li>行内式是将JavaScript代码作为HTML标签的属性值使用。</li>\n</ul><blockquote>\n<p> 例如    </p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>单击“test”时，弹出一个警告框提示“Happy”。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;a href=<span class=\"string\">\"javascript:alert('Happy');\"</span>&gt; test &lt;<span class=\"regexp\">/a&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>单击网页中的一个按钮时，就会触发按钮的单击事件。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;input type=<span class=\"string\">\"button\"</span> onclick=<span class=\"string\">\"alert('Happy'); \"</span> value=<span class=\"string\">\"test\"</span> &gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"嵌入式\">嵌入式<a href=\"#嵌入式\" title=\"嵌入式\"></a></h2><p> 在HTML中运用<code>&lt;script&gt;</code>标签及其相关属性可以嵌入JavaScript脚本代码。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;<span class=\"selector-tag\">head</span>&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;script type=\"text/javascript\"&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     // 此处为JavaScript代码</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/script&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/head&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"外链式\">外链式<a href=\"#外链式\" title=\"外链式\"></a></h2><ul><li><p>外链式是将所有的JavaScript代码放在一个或多个以<code>.js</code>为扩展名的外部JavaScript文件中，通过<code>&lt;src &gt;</code>标签将这些JavaScript文件链接到HTML文档中</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在编写JavaScript代码时可以省略type属性</p>\n</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;script type=<span class=\"string\">\"text/Javascript\"</span> src=<span class=\"string\">\"脚本文件路径\"</span> &gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;<span class=\"regexp\">/script&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote>\n<p>优势</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol><li>利于后期修改和维护</li>\n<li>减轻文件体积、加快页面加载速度</li>\n</ol><h1 id=\"变量\">变量<a href=\"#变量\" title=\"变量\"></a></h1><p>在<strong>程序运行期间</strong>，随时可能产生一些<strong>临时数据</strong>，应用程序会将这些数据保存在一些<strong>内存单元</strong>中。变量就是指程序中一个已经命名的<strong>存储单元</strong>，它的主要作用就是为<strong>数据操作</strong>提供<strong>存放信息的容器</strong>。</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201130093747.png\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" />","next":{"title":"过渡、变形和动画","link":"posts/540576d8"},"plink":"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/1b3d4e9a/","toc":[{"id":"javascript的引入","title":"JavaScript的引入","index":"1","children":[{"id":"行内式","title":"行内式","index":"1.1"},{"id":"嵌入式","title":"嵌入式","index":"1.2"},{"id":"外链式","title":"外链式","index":"1.3"}]},{"id":"变量","title":"变量","index":"2"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"DxSummer","link":"<a href=\"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/1b3d4e9a/\" title=\"绘图和数据存储原理\">https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/1b3d4e9a/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"2020年11月30日","updated":"2020年11月30日"}}